Author: Quesokinesis
Text: Look at you, though, showing those bitches who's boss. Assert that fuckin *dominance.*  Had my first Mother's Day without my mom, and spent it traveling. Ate everything besides the freeway itself. Ate shit I haven't eaten in *years.* Grief is a weird demon...it makes me feel so empty inside, but not airy, light emptiness. Empty like a vacuum.  Solidarity. Hope you find a bit of peace soon, Ortho.

Author: RaineeRose
Text: This is too real. :(  Sending hugs.
